{"tid":407780,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貧血保母偷飲台靚媽母乳 「喝一斤奶補一斤血」","createTime":"2017-09-20T16:41:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T17:46:21.000Z","uid":29627,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f459b10fe5dcbbdf8ea745a56787ce2829f58f22","tid":407780,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:41:01.000Z","msg":"忍無可忍！台灣高雄一名林姓母親近日發現，本來給女兒填肚的母乳，竟被鄭姓保母（58歲）偷喝了。林女稱，該保母毫無悔意，辯稱自己貧血，喝一斤奶等於給自己補一斤血。高雄市府社會局獲悉後，認為不構成重大違規，保留她的保母資格。至於飲母乳是否真否有補氣血之效，《蘋果》專訪本港中、西醫了解真相！<br />\n<br />\n林女在坐月時聘請保母照顧女嬰，並在家中客廳安裝監控鏡頭，結果卻拍到了保母趁她暫時離開時，偷喝其母乳的畫面。影片顯示，保母發現奶樽還剩50c.c.母乳，隔不到5分鐘就將女嬰放到床上，此時的奶樽卻空空如也，育嬰日誌則記錄女嬰喝完130c.c.母乳。<br />\n<br />\n原來，保母在她入房後，就抱着女嬰走到雪櫃旁死角處，將母乳喝掉，且沒有為女兒打嗝，事後還騙說女嬰全部喝完了。當林女與保母對質時，保母指林女跟其他媽媽不一樣，她上一個僱主還特意給自己母乳讓她帶回家喝，而林女這麼跟她計較。<br />\n<br />\n高雄市府社會局表示，鄭姓保母行為確實有違居家保母規定，但未傷及寶寶不構成重大違規，已要求她限期改善。這事讓林女十分生氣，覺得保母的行為不但是對自己女兒不負責任，也是對自己的不尊重。<br />\n<br />\n對成年人喝母乳，高雄醫學大學附設醫院婦產部產科主任陳鴻昇指出，大人喝母乳對健康並沒有額外幫助，此外母乳很稀有，是寶寶珍貴的營養品，應盡量給寶寶喝，給大人喝太浪費。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170921/57232401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170921%2F57232401&d=Saleply5TRv7NA95VFOxydtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=2a4c4695\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170921%2F57232401&h=7db54eab\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170921/57232401</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170920/large/1505914716_5f3c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170920%2Flarge%2F1505914716_5f3c.jpg&h=4f208b49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170920/large/1505914727_92b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170920%2Flarge%2F1505914727_92b3.jpg&h=643d6511&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170920/large/1505914728_5628.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170920%2Flarge%2F1505914728_5628.jpg&h=6f84dfb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6448229b05a72d84026614b68ba3fbe24c2dc3bd","tid":407780,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"我都想飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103d24f2fc4acc8e615806a69365761b2738c7e9","tid":407780,"uid":44559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:48:30.000Z","msg":"呃喂左奶，一陣餓瓜bb 咪仆街"},{"pid":"d7e63a1e51151b1fdcb76ae267a7924d6e8fb5f3","tid":407780,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T16:54:16.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55d87e0c37544a7c3ea8d71b24225e4cd554164","tid":407780,"uid":15309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"我都想飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf578efb4b12917cb69b8f1ed9c03912acbbb6a8","tid":407780,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/faces/lomore/tongue3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Ffaces%2Flomore%2Ftongue3.gif&h=04906a0b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/faces/lomore/tongue3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u